@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@existingUserId = 2
@invalidUserId = 0
@missingUserId = 999999

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：获取用户详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{existingUserId}}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录获取用户详情，预期 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{existingUserId}}

### 异常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：普通员工获取用户详情，预期 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{existingUserId}}

### 异常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：user_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{invalidUserId}}

### 异常路径：用户不存在，预期 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{missingUserId}}
